Do I have to kill him?

291
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,640
It's not that simple.

292
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,900
You beat him in the illusion just now.

293
00:12:00,040 --> 00:12:01,240
Best two out of three.

294
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:03,580
You need to beat him one more time.

295
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:04,960
Boss,

296
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:06,360
let's go.

297
00:12:06,520 --> 00:12:08,250
According to the reward rules,

298
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:10,720
from the illusion just now,

299
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:12,640
you can make a wish

300
00:12:12,880 --> 00:12:14,340
and bring it into reality.

301
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:17,840
Then...

302
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:19,300
Then resurrect my mother.

303
00:12:19,560 --> 00:12:21,080
Be realistic.

304
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,400
Realistic?

305
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:24,600
For this family,

306
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:26,370
I really have no expectations.

307
00:12:27,760 --> 00:12:28,620
How about this?

308
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:43,840
Thanks.

309
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:53,760
Wait.

310
00:12:57,400 --> 00:12:58,520
What's that sound?

311
00:12:59,120 --> 00:12:59,960
Is it thunder?

312
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,930
Thunder wouldn't be this regular.

313
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:09,880
There is a formation set by a great demon isolating this space.

314
00:13:09,880 --> 00:13:10,760
Outside,

315
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:13,200
they must have started attacking this place.

316
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,200
This sound,

317
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:16,040
is someone ramming the door.

318
00:13:16,040 --> 00:13:16,840
They...

319
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:20,760
I urged them to unite a long time ago.

320
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:24,360
Now they're finally showing what they can do.

321
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:25,320
Maybe

322
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:27,850
you lacked some persuasion skills back then.

323
00:13:28,040 --> 00:13:29,170
Let's help them out.

324
00:13:31,640 --> 00:13:33,900
I am Lin Mo, the new head of the Lin family.

325
00:13:33,920 --> 00:13:34,800
Today

326
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:36,440
is a joyous day for our Lin family.

327
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:38,160
I order everyone in the Lin family

328
00:13:38,160 --> 00:13:39,840
to open the doors and welcome the guests.

329
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:40,800
Move aside!

330
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:44,840
Move that junk away.

331
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,400
My second brother is breaking the door!

332
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:47,320
Here I come.

333
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,680
My life's

334
00:13:48,680 --> 00:13:50,080
strongest sword strike!

335
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:21,650
Second Brother.

336
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,600
I don't want to ruin your mood,

337
00:14:23,800 --> 00:14:24,640
but right now,

338
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:26,360
it seems we don't need you.

